name: Mary Frantz
description: I am a very honest and loyal woman, looking for the same in You….I like to laugh, joke, and have fun, but i can be serious when the occasions calls for it.I am versatile on trying new experiences.Can go from one end of the spectrum to the other on many things.i hope You are intelligent, sincere and a caring man..well my mother told me to love a man and treat him just like me…this have been on my mine since i was a little girl
